      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Executive\n\n---\n\n### [Portfolio Health](/d/nce-safe-portfolio-health)\nValue stream health traffic lights, at-risk epics, and top blocked items.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n### [WSJF Priority Board](/d/nce-safe-wsjf)\nWeighted Shortest Job First scoring \u2014 ranked candidates and full scoring table.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n### [Risk Register](/d/nce-safe-risk-register)\nROAM risk distribution and behind-schedule items.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n### [Flow Metrics](/d/nce-safe-flow-metrics)\nPI velocity, predictability %, committed vs delivered."
      },
